[p][b]Generals[/b]![/p][p][/p][p]Allied Headquarters has organised a fresh task force, the [url="https://pdxint.at/hoi4ge"]General Edition[/url]![/p][p][/p][p]This offers the [b]Base Game[/b], [b]La Résistance[/b], and [b]Battle for the Bosporus[/b], minus [b]Man the Guns[/b] on account of it being free, in advance of full integration into the base game when [b]No Compromise[/b], [b]No Surrender[/b] launches.[/p][p][/p][p]Reinforce your Steam library with [url="https://store.steampowered.com/app/815460/Expansion__Hearts_of_Iron_IV_Man_the_Guns/"][b]Man the Guns[/b][/url], now![/p][p][/p][p][/p][p][dynamiclink href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/815460/Expansion__Hearts_of_Iron_IV_Man_the_Guns/"][/dynamiclink][dynamiclink href="https://store.steampowered.com/sub/1429184/"][/dynamiclink][/p][p][/p]